* Mole dependent material: InGaAs (x=0) = InAs
* Mole dependent material: InGaAs (x=1) = GaAs


Epsilon
{ 
  * Ratio of the permittivities of material and vacuum
  * epsilon() = epsilon

  *	epsilon(0)	= 15.1	# [1] # [Ioffe]
  *	epsilon(1)	= 12.9	# [1] # [Ioffe]
  *	B(epsilon(1)) = 0.67  # [Ioffe]

	epsilon(0)	= 14.3	# [1] # [05Ada]
	epsilon(1)	= 12.9	# [1] # [05Ada]
}

